{"tid":290394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你嗰局象棋仲有幾多步就被將死？","createTime":"2017-06-19T17:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T17:55:54.000Z","uid":117576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10cbf548b8cbdff9ed63c6a8d193db964f4760e1","tid":290394,"uid":117576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:39:27.000Z","msg":"人生同捉象棋無異，起手既時候猶如童年，腦入面有好多把對方將死 將夢想成真既美好畫面，你唔知個過程係點，但你以為只要坐出隻炮 就可以&quot;重炮將&quot;到對方。 但時間一耐，你會發現個社會下下都想食你啲棋，佢想食你隻兵，你就搵隻馬睇住，佢想食你隻馬，你就搵隻車睇住⋯⋯ 最後動彈不得，唔好話重炮，你連租都俾唔起，時間唔會停，你亦都冇悔棋或者慢慢諗下一步既時間，慢慢你就俾個社會將軍抽車，你再睇唔住隻馬，最後兵都俾人食埋，慢慢俾人屈死，你？你仲有幾多步就被將死？"},{"pid":"c0401d38152c3e1063d1539fa89dbd8cd44cf258","tid":290394,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:49:01.000Z","msg":"我應該捉緊一場只會輸，唔會贏既棋"},{"pid":"18028631b696fa7c43456e046e2e0c07cb46e9cf","tid":290394,"uid":71541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:51:54.000Z","msg":"一開頭已經讓左雙車比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152d9e279b98120217fe420bac3bd415fa97a542","tid":290394,"uid":117576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:54:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開頭已經讓左雙車比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唉，無錢冇樣"},{"pid":"0d3d42591e5d0f6b25d3db41a47aaee2429e42e8","tid":290394,"uid":117576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我應該捉緊一場只會輸，唔會贏既棋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阿Q精神，起碼我有捉過盤棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}